name: elm-fontawesome-example
description: Example usage of the elm-fontawesome package.

scripts.build: elm make src/Example.elm --optimize --output=example.js && npx uglifyjs example.js --compress 'pure_funcs="F2,F3,F4,F5,F6,F7,F8,F9,A2,A3,A4,A5,A6,A7,A8,A9",pure_getters,keep_fargs=false,unsafe_comps,unsafe' | uglifyjs --mangle --output dist/example.js

author: Gareth Latty <gareth@lattyware.co.uk>
